This paper deals with machine learning in repeated stochastic games, which involves both game theory and reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GT (Game Theory), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
